title: SIC! SIC ! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC ! SIC!

“The fates of two massive proposals to ease conjection in the city centre... are still undecided.” [From New Statesman & Society, 6 July 1990, p. 16. Submitted by M. Gautrey, Geneva.]
